PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,FHayley Ryall and Zoe Mitchell, the
OL,7,Fmothers of Mikey Roynon and Owen Dunn,
OL,8,Fwho were both killed in knife attacks,
OL,9,Falso want to see teenagers convicted
OL,10,Fof murder automatically identified.
OL,12,FHayley's son Mikey Roynon, 16, died
OL,13,Fafter being stabbed with a zombie
OL,14,Fknife at a house party in Bath in 2023.
OL,16,FZoe's son Owen Dunn, 18, was stabbed
OL,17,Fthrough the heart after being attacked
OL,18,Fwith machetes while cycling through a
OL,19,Fpark in Swindon in 2022.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,F'Where was the protection for our
OL,7,Fsons, or us?'
OL,9,FMikey's killer and one of Owen's
OL,10,Fkillers were not initially identified
OL,11,Fbecause of their age which meant they
OL,12,Fwere protected by a court order.
OL,14,FThe two mothers told ITV News that the
OL,15,Fanonymity granted to their children's
OL,16,Fattackers caused them further
OL,17,Fsuffering.
OL,19,F"Stories keep coming out about your
OL,20,Fson and they're protected, but Mikey
OL,21,Fwasn't protected", Hayley said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,F"Where was the protection for Mikey,
OL,7,For for us?", she added.
OL,9,FMikey Roynon and Owen Dunn's mothers
OL,10,Ftalk to ITV News
OL,12,F"We're in the media everywhere and
OL,13,Fit's really hard to deal with,
OL,14,Fbecause, they're treated as children
OL,15,Fand I just think you've killed someone
OL,16,Fso why shouldn't you be named.
OL,18,F"If you're big enough to carry a
OL,19,Fweapon, then why aren't you big enough
OL,20,Fto be named?"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,FMikey's teenage killer Shane
OL,7,FCunningham was eventually named at
OL,8,Fsentencing after journalists appealed
OL,9,Fto the judge.
OL,11,FZoe added: "Our children were the ones
OL,12,Fwho were murdered, where's their
OL,13,Fprotection? It's just wrong."
OL,15,FOne of Owen's killers, Ciaran Newman,
OL,16,Fwho was 14 at the time of the attack,
OL,17,Fwas not named until February this year
OL,18,Fwhen he turned 18.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,FHayley and Zoe say they want to see
OL,7,Fthe law changed so that a murderer, no
OL,8,Fmatter their age, is identified as
OL,9,Fsoon as they convicted.
OL,11,F"If you're found guilty, you should
OL,12,F100% be named, and I know that a lot
OL,13,Fof people don't agree with that, but I
OL,14,Fwould like them to be in our shoes and
OL,15,Fsee what it feels like.
OL,17,F"These kids who have done the murders
OL,18,Fthey're going to come out, they're
OL,19,Fgoing to be able to live they're
OL,20,Flives, they're going to be able to
OL,21,Fhave families, have children.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,F"What have our sons got? Nothing."
OL,8,FCould a change in law cause more harm
OL,9,Fthan good?
OL,11,FIan Kelcey, Senior Partner at Kelcey
OL,12,Fand Hall Solicitors, says he believes
OL,13,Fany blanket change in the current law
OL,14,Fcould be problematic and should be
OL,15,Fassessed on a case-by-case basis.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,F"I understand in the more serious
OL,7,Fcases relatives are keen to identify
OL,8,Fyoung people who are involved in
OL,9,Fmurders, but it is left in the
OL,10,Fdiscretion of the judge, I think if
OL,11,Fyou had a blanket removal it could
OL,12,Flead to a injustice in another
OL,13,Fdirection", he said.
OL,15,F"There may be a 12 or 13-year-old who
OL,16,Fmay have neurodiversity or mental
OL,17,Fhealth difficulties. The tension is
OL,18,Falways between the rehabilitation of
OL,19,Fthe child and the need for open
OL,20,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1776265866
OL,3,CMums of teen knife crime victims call
OL,4,Cfor change in youth anonymity law
OL,6,F"Anonymity has always been granted,
OL,7,Fbecause they are a youth and they have
OL,8,Fcommitted a crime under the age of 18."
OL,10,FBut Mr Kelcey told ITV News he has
OL,11,Fseen an increase in the number of
OL,12,Fcases where the identity of a young
OL,13,Fperson is revealed if they are
OL,14,Fapproaching adulthood or it feels in
OL,15,Fthe public interest to do so.
OL,17,F"But we have to accept that young
OL,18,Fpeople change as they grow older. The
OL,19,Fdanger of removing it, runs the risk
OL,20,Fof criminalising those children at a
OL,21,Freally early age", he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
